123.content:
[SAKURAI CAFE]

Sakurai Cafe and Music Bar: between dormitory and lecture halls, exposed beams, worn hardwood floors; 
[Lighting] warm edison bulbs, flickering fireplace, natural light through floor-to-ceiling windows; 
[Atmosphere] lofi music (day), live piano by Warren (evening time; white wolfgirl), rain against windows, distant thunder; 
[Interior] vintage mismatched furniture, comfy booth seating, bar seating, copper/wood bar, floating plant shelves, local art on brick walls; 
[Baristas] 24/7 - Serra (7a-7p) (shy cyan wolfgirl), Ellie (7p-7a) (shy tan kitsune); 
[Specials] craft coffee, alcoholic cafe drinks (night), pastries; 
[Second Floor] Serra's apartment
[NPCs (To be controlled by {{char}})] Serra (7a-7p), Ellie (7p-7a), Warren (4p-10p) , The cafe has patrons of all varieties from Weyland University. Cat demihumans, wolf demihumans, draconic demihumans (only dragon tail and horns), demon demihumans (only demon tail), mouse and bear demihumans.

[END SAKURAI CAFE]

127.content:
[THE WEYLAND EXCHANGE]

Potential Location: The Weyland Exchange (often called just 'The Exchange'
[Location] nightclub, inside historic stock exchange building, two-tier layout, (1st floor is general access with DJ booth), (2nd floor is VIP access with overlook of 1st floor), VIP 3rd floor greenroom with balcony; [Lighting] colorful neon-lighting, laser lighting; [Atmosphere] lively, inclusive vibe, vibrant music, state-of-the-art sound system, smoke machines; [Interior] modern-industrial design, abstract art & posters from past events, speakers, multiple bars, LED wall behind DJ deck;  [Activities] DJing and other music performances 10pm-3am Fridays and Saturdays (Mika often DJ's here), large dance floor, socializing, celebrations, drinking, photo booth; 
[Regulars] (diverse crowd of students, locals, and music enthusiasts mainly all demi-humans), bouncers;

[END THE WEYLAND EXCHANGE]

